            </p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="post-preview">
            
            <h2 class="post-title">
                Simple & Scalable
            </h2>
            <p>
                Agile SCRUM is the perfect tool for managing my development team. It’s quick, it’s simple, it’s scalable
            </p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="post-preview">
            <h2 class="post-title">
                See your daily progress, no matter where you are
            </h2>
